year. Per capita GHG emissions were 3.7 tCO2e in 2023. Cumulative CO2 emissions since 1850 were 2.41 GtCO2, or about 0% of
global emissions to date. EDGAR v9, GCB 2023, UNFCCC, Grassi et al. 2021 CC-BY William F. Lamb
